Troubleshooting Tips
SpiderFoot won't start:

Check if port 5001 is already in use: netstat -tuln | grep 5001
Kill existing process: pkill -f sf.py
Verify Python dependencies: pip3 install -r requirements.txt
recon-ng module installation fails:

Update recon-ng: cd recon-ng && git pull
Check internet connectivity
Try installing modules individually
DNS queries return no results:

Verify DNS server is reachable: ping 8.8.8.8
Use alternative DNS: dig @8.8.8.8 example.com
Check if domain exists and is properly configured
Script permission errors:

Ensure scripts are executable: chmod +x script_name.py
Check file ownership: ls -l script_name.py
Run with explicit Python: python3 script_name.py
